            Texas flood updates
          </h2>
        </mj-text>
        <mj-image
          border-radius="10px"
          padding="10px 12px"
          width="600px"
          src="https://www.presidentialsummary.com/email/images/kerr-county-flood-warning-siren-plan-failed.jpg"
